@startuml
title Viaverse Business Subscription / Billing — Activity Diagram
start
:Business selects plan;
:Check eligibility\nbusiness publish state;
if (Trial available?) then (yes)
  :Start first-month trial;
else (no)
  :Collect payment method\nif required;
endif
:Create billing profile\nplan + invoice cycle;
:Activate subscription;
:Apply feature gates\nleads/ads/insights;
:Renewal date reached;
:Charge provider;
if (Paid?) then (yes)
  :Emit subscription events;
else (no)
  :Dunning / grace period;
  :Limit business features;
  :Emit subscription events;
endif
stop

note bottom
Plan, trial length, monthly price, free rights and feature gates must be admin-configurable;
do not hardcode 500 TL or trial duration in business logic.
end note
@enduml
